<div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 pt-3 pb-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <section class="bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
      <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.25fr_1fr] lg:items-center">
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">새로 만난 단어와 표현을 차곡차곡 모아보세요</h1>
            <p class="text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">외우고 싶은 단어, 헷갈리는 용어, 자주 쓰는 표현을 항목으로 저장하고 그룹과 메모로 다시 찾기 쉽게 정리하세요.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <%= link_to "새 항목 추가", new_post_path, class: "inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-500" %>
            <%= link_to "항목 목록 보기", posts_path, class: "inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-50" %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 p-4 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">정리 방식</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">항목과 그룹</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">주제별 그룹으로 나누어 단어와 용어를 빠르게 찾아보세요.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-green-50 p-4 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">기억 보조</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">메모와 댓글</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">예문, 뉘앙스, 떠오른 생각을 남겨 복습할 단서를 쌓아두세요.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">최근 학습 항목</h2>
        </div>
        <%= link_to "전체 보기", posts_path, class: "text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-500" %>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
        <% if @recent_posts.any? %>
          <% @recent_posts.each do |post| %>
            <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md">
              <%= link_to post_path(post), class: "block text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 hover:text-blue-600" do %>
                <%= truncate(post.title, length: 50) %>
              <% end %>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500"><%= post.user.display_name %> · 댓글 <%= post.comments.count %></p>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600"><%= truncate(post.body, length: 90) %></p>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% else %>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-dashed border-slate-300 bg-white p-6 text-center text-slate-500">
            아직 저장된 항목이 없습니다.<br>
            <%= link_to "첫 항목을 추가해보세요", new_post_path, class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-500" %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
